title = {{COSMIC DISTANCES CALIBRATED TO 1% PRECISION WITH GAIA EDR3 PARALLAXES AND HUBBLE SPACE TELESCOPE PHOTOMETRY OF 75 MILKY WAY CEPHEIDS CONFIRM TENSION WITH $\Lambda$CDM}},
